findings.suggested_fix:
In the new opcert SSM parameter resource:
```hcl
resource "aws_ssm_parameter" "opcert_ed25519_key" {
  name  = "/rebar/prod/opcert-ed25519-key"
  type  = "SecureString"
  value = "CHANGEME"

  lifecycle {
    ignore_changes  = [value]
    prevent_destroy = true   # sole copy of the trust anchor — accidental destroy is irrecoverable
  }
}
```
